{"tid":798679,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遲到港媽鬧爆的哥︰等10分鐘都呱呱嘈 網民派嬲","createTime":"2018-08-29T12:51:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T12:57:46.000Z","uid":80516,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9ad6561429a53645359e31ab8d4042a7ab5774a3","tid":798679,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KIV_FZc32_SS13sICQOpsA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/1c292bf50f6dd4408c48ebbea31eca3a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FKIV_FZc32_SS13sICQOpsA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F1c292bf50f6dd4408c48ebbea31eca3a&h=2238d1f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等待遲到的人，你最多可以包容幾耐？近日有港媽在其社交網站發貼，斥的士司機等候她十分鐘後，對她「呱呱嘈」，服務態度惡劣。<br />\n<br />\n貼文指，有日滂沱大雨，該媽媽一手拖着女兒，一手捧着蛋糕，惟她到達與的士司機的約定地點時，遲了約10分鐘。她指當時司機不斷「呱呱嘈」︰「我（司機）以為你落咗樓下等我，要我等番你轉頭」。<br />\n<br />\n她批評司機態度惡劣︰「我心諗，你咁趕可以走先，我Call（電召）另一架的士！的士司機給些好的服務可以嗎」。<br />\n<br />\n貼文其後在網絡瘋傳，不少網民力撐的士司機︰「人哋搵食，老奉等你咩」、「Call車當足係私人司機」、「要人等你，理應叫人起錶計錢才合理」。又有人建議該媽媽可多付小費，而非放上網責罵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180829/bkn-20180829121025160-0829_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180829%2Fbkn-20180829121025160-0829_00822_001.html&d=c%2BU9SroH3bzlC3xuuhKPfB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=04d19b37\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180829/bkn-20180829121025160-0829_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d2a2e9e6d793ddae99dbde4beaef8ffd92c702fa","tid":798679,"uid":99568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:53:09.000Z","msg":"打和啦super"},{"pid":"bc4b8df9113a42b6375e3a6b632641e0b98e52b3","tid":798679,"uid":168331,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12